


(1) Possible combination to run:  

   3dboxper.par, 3dboxper.re2, 3dboxper.co2
   3dboxper.rea, 3dboxper.re2, 3dboxper.co2
   3dboxper.rea, 3dboxper.re2, 3dboxper.map
   3dboxper.rea, 3dboxper.re2, 3dboxper.ma2

(2)
  mesh/param setting  : 3dboxper.rea (fully ascii with no re2) -- I didn't put this case here.
  mesh/param setting  : 3dboxper.par  + 3dboxper.re2 (binary)
  mesh/param setting  : 3dboxper.rea  + 3dboxper.re2 (e.g., "-128" elements in reafile )
  mesh connetivity    : 3dboxper.map or 3dboxper.ma2 or 3dboxper.co2
 

  3dboxper.rea with binary re2 file (e.g., "-128" elements in reafile )
  **MESH DATA** 6 lines are X,Y,Z;X,Y,Z. Columns corners 1-4;5-8
        -128  3           128     NELT,NDIM,NELV

